      <title>Introduction</title>
      <link>https://ksu-cs-textbooks.github.io/cs-zero/i-concepts/10-hci/01-introduction/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Aug 2020 16:27:26 -0500</pubDate>
      <guid>https://ksu-cs-textbooks.github.io/cs-zero/i-concepts/10-hci/01-introduction/</guid>
      <description>YouTube Video Resources Slides Video Script In this module, we&amp;rsquo;ll discuss the field of human computer interaction or HCI, sometimes referred to as computer human interaction, or CHI. It is the study of how computers and humans interact and how we design computers to better support humans in that efforts. HCI is one of the fields that we&amp;rsquo;re going to look at it throughout the semester, we&amp;rsquo;ll do this several times.</description>
    </item>
    <item>
